
Dependencies

Python version: 3.10+

Major libraries:

Library	Purpose
numpy	Matrix operations, complex numbers
pandas	CSV reading/writing, data handling
matplotlib	Plotting DOA, SNR, and beam patterns
scipy	Signal processing (Savitzky–Golay, pinv)
scikit-learn	Optional: if ML models are added later

Optional extras if you expand your ML workflow:
seaborn – nicer plots
jupyter – for notebooks
plotly – interactive 3D beam patterns
